                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7637" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1192</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3277 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“黑马突围”：胡姬花的市场抢位战</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Dark Horse Breakthrough”：HuJihua&#39;s Market Position Competition</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">代碧波，陈晓菲，宋国宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨商业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">益海嘉里食品营销有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">竞争格局；产品差异化战略；市场抢位；品类创新；2023百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Competitive pattern；Product differentiation strategy；Market share grabbing；Category innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通过描述益海嘉里“胡姬花”如何从“鲁花”占据花生油市场半壁江山到与“鲁花”平分秋色这一市场竞争格局的转变过程，展示出“胡姬花”在激烈的市场竞争下如何锁定竞争对手、通过市场细分准确定位消费需求，从而实现市场突围的“解构-重构”过程。案例进一步揭示了“胡姬花”为获取市场地位，通过品类创新战略挑战市场领导地位，进行“市场抢位”并突出重围的内在逻辑，并探讨“胡姬花”在面对竞争对手和消费者需求变化时如何继续保持品牌竞争力。本案例旨在启发学生对粮油食品企业如何在市场竞争中面向消费需求升级进行战略重构和营销创新的思考，使学生学会分析企业竞争背后的行为逻辑，从而增强对市场需求变化和竞争行为的分析与创新能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This describes the transformation process of Yihai Kerry&#39;s “Hujihua” from “Luhua” occupying half of the peanut oil market to the market competition pattern of “Hujihua” and “Luhua” sharing equally， it shows how “Hujihua”locked in competitors under fierce market competition，accurately positioned consumer demand through market segmentation，so as to achieve the “deconstruction -reconstruction” process of market breakthrough. The case further reveals “Hujihua” challenges market leadership to further gain market position through category innovation strategies，carries out “market share grabbing” and highlights the inherent logic of encirclement，and explores how “Hujihua” can continue to maintain brand competitiveness in the face of changes in competitors and consumer demand. The purpose of this case is to inspire students to think about how grain，oil and food enterprises can strategically restructure and innovate marketing in order to upgrade consumer demand in market competition. This will enable students to learn to analyze the behavioral logic behind enterprise competition，thereby enhancing their ability to analyze and innovate changes in market demand and competitive behavior.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产品差异化战略；品类创新；场结构与企业行为；SWOT分析；竞争优势</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
